pr_title: RepositoryUtility.findHighestVersion to work with non-semantic version

timeline.bodyText: As per https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/MAVENOLD/Dependency+Mediation+and+Conflict+Resolution#DependencyMediationandConflictResolution-DependencyVersionRanges, both min and max are optional. We didn't have to specify the minimum limit.
timeline.author: suztomo
